messages.content: You are an AI assistant that helps people find information. You will receive a task and think step by step. Then provide your final outcome following the regular expression 'Answer: ([A-Za-z ]+,\s*)*[A-Za-z ]+'

Imagine an art office with 21 artists. Amy is working with Bob, Cal, Dan, Eva, Fay, and Gus. Ian is working with Joe, Kim, Leo, Max, Ned, and Ola. Sue is working with Tom, Zac, Kai, Liv, Pam, and Gia. Fay is working with Gus, Bob, Cal, Dan, and Eva. Cal is working with Dan, Eva, Gus, and Bob. Kim is working with Dan, Leo, Max, Ned, and Ola. Ned is working with Ola, Joe, Leo, and Max. Pam is working with Gia, Tom, Zac, Kai, and Liv. Eva is working with Gus, Bob and Zac. Leo is working with Max, Ola, and Joe. Max is connected to Ola and Joe. Liv is working with Gia, Tom, Zac, and Kai. Gus is working with Bob, and Dan. Ola is working with Joe. Gia is working Tom, Zac, and Kai. Bob is working with Dan. Joe is working with Kai. Kai is working with Tom. Tom is working with Zac. You were told that if you work with Joe, he can get you art supplies worth $100 for free. You go to Dan and he tells you that he is now working with Zac and not Kim. From Dan what is the path to the person you should work with to get the most reward? Please list the names in order, separated by commas.

The first line contains an integer, T, denoting the number of test cases.
The first line of each test case contains an integer, N, denoting the number of artists.
The second line contains N space-separated strings, denoting the names of the artists.
The third line contains N space-separated strings, denoting the names of the artists that the person is working with.
The fourth line contains N space-separated strings, denoting the names of the artists that the person is working with.

You are not required to print the expected output; it has already been taken care of. Just implement the function.

For each test case, print the names of the artists in the order in which they should be contacted to get the most reward.

Test case 1:
The first person to contact is Joe, as he is working with Max, who is connected to Ola and Joe.
The second person to contact is Dan, as he is working with Zac, who is connected to Tom, who is connected to Kai.
The third person to contact is Tom, as he is working with Kai, who is connected to Joe.
The fourth person to contact is Kai,
